landingProducts.name: Annie's Organic Cinnamon Rolls with Icing

productInfo.details:
Sweeten up your morning with Annie's Organic Cinnamon Rolls! Made with the goodness you'd expect from Annie's, our yummy cinnamon rolls have quality ingredients and no artificial flavors, synthetic colors, or high fructose corn syrup. They're also certified USDA Organic and non-GMO. Even sweeter, our ready-to-bake cinnamon rolls come with a squeeze-on icing pouch to top them with deliciousness. Simply place dough flat on a cookie sheet and bake at 350 degrees for about 18 to 20 minutes. Cool slightly, then squeeze on the creamy icing and prepare to devour. This pack of 3 cans makes a total of 15 organic cinnamon rolls. Annie's makes products in over 20 family-friendly categories, from fruit flavored snacks and cereal to mac and cheese. For busy bunnies and families on the go, we help make life a little easier and more delicious by spreading goodness through tasty foods and kindness to the planet. 
 
• TASTY CINNAMON ROLLS: This dough is ready to bake and comes with a squeeze-on icing pouch; Enjoy irresistible cinnamon flavor in every bite
 
• SWEET TREAT FOR EVERYBUNNY: Your family will come hopping for this delicious breakfast addition; Try serving as a yummy, cinnamon-y dessert
 
• CERTIFIED ORGANIC: Certified USDA Organic and non-GMO for the goodness you'd expect from Annie's
 
• QUICK AND EASY: This 3 pack of ready-to-bake cinnamon rolls refrigerated canned dough makes it easy to whip up a sweet part of breakfast in minutes
 
• CONTAINS: One 52.5 oz pack of Annie's Organic Cinnamon Rolls with Icing; Three 17.5 oz cans inside; Makes a total of 15 cinnamon rolls
